name: Rick and Morty: The Anime
overview: It's life mostly as usual for the Smith family. Rick is in a pseudo-world, Summer helps Space Beth and Morty's in love. And they're all an anime.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: In season 1, Rick relaxes in a pseudo-world between multiverses, Summer helps Space Beth fight the evil Galactic Federation, and Morty falls in love with a mysterious girl who happens to be an atemporal being.

episodes.name: Girl Who Manipulates Time
episodes.overview: In this new universe, Morty falls in love with a new girl. And the Galactic Federation goes after Rick and his mysterious device.

episodes.name: Fighting Mother
episodes.overview: Rick is captured by the Federation. Space Beth is on the case. And so is Rick. And Rick.

episodes.name: Alien Elle
episodes.overview: Morty takes the fight to the Federation. And Morty looks for love in all the wrong places.

episodes.name: Memories
episodes.overview: Summer and Morty search for Rick while he's trapped in a multiverse. Also, Jerry goes missing.

episodes.name: Family
episodes.overview: Jerry does something bad, or maybe it's good? So now the Yakuza are after the Smiths.

episodes.name: Free Will
episodes.overview: Morty and Elle are reunited. But what are Space Beth and Rick hiding...

episodes.name: When We Meet in Our Dreams
episodes.overview: When a Morty goes down, a Rick takes action. Nothing bad could happen to the universe, right?

episodes.name: Feel, Don't Think
episodes.overview: As the Smith family prepares for a fight, Rick reveals a hidden truth to Morty.

episodes.name: Her Innermost Wish
episodes.overview: The Smith family battles the Federation. Elle vows to protect Morty, but what about Rick?

episodes.name: A Pain in the Back
episodes.overview: Morty might finally be at peace. But Space Morty might be in real trouble.
